<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/32369989">南北朝隋唐时期为什么人名里面多一些固定的字，如僧、客等？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="5147523" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">比如，王僧辩、宗楚客。</div>


</div>
